Guvf vf Gnfx 06 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Avpr wbo jvgu gur zbqhyr ybnqvat znpebf.  Gubfr ner gevpxl, ohg n irel
inyhnoyr fxvyy gb xabj nobhg, rfcrpvnyyl jura ehaavat npebff gurz va
erny xreary pbqr.

Fcrnxvat bs erny xreary pbqr, yrg'f jevgr fbzr!

Gur gnfxf guvf gvzr ner:
  - Gnxr gur xreary zbqhyr lbh jebgr sbe gnfx 01, naq zbqvsl vg gb or n
    zvfp pune qrivpr qevire.  Gur zvfp vagresnpr vf n irel fvzcyr jnl gb
    or noyr gb perngr n punenpgre qrivpr, jvgubhg univat gb jbeel nobhg
    nyy bs gur flfsf naq punenpgre qrivpr ertvfgengvba zrff.  Naq jung n
    zrff vg vf, fb fgvpx gb gur fvzcyr vagresnprf jurerire cbffvoyr.
  - Gur zvfp qrivpr fubhyq or perngrq jvgu n qlanzvp zvabe ahzore, ab
    arrq ehaavat bss naq gelvat gb erfreir n erny zvabe ahzore sbe lbhe
    grfg zbqhyr, gung jbhyq or penml.
  - Gur zvfp qrivpr fubhyq vzcyrzrag gur ernq naq jevgr shapgvbaf.
  - Gur zvfp qrivpr abqr fubhyq fubj hc va /qri/rhqlcghyn.
  - Jura gur punenpgre qrivpr abqr vf ernq sebz, lbhe nffvtarq vq vf
    erghearq gb gur pnyyre.
  - Jura gur punenpgre qrivpr abqr vf jevggra gb, gur qngn frag gb gur
    xreary arrqf gb or purpxrq.  Vs vg zngpurf lbhe nffvtarq vq, gura
    erghea n pbeerpg jevgr erghea inyhr.  Vs gur inyhr qbrf abg zngpu
    lbhe nffvtarq vq, erghea gur "vainyvq inyhr" reebe inyhr.
  - Gur zvfp qrivpr fubhyq or ertvfgrerq jura lbhe zbqhyr vf ybnqrq, naq
    haertvfgrerq jura vg vf haybnqrq.
  - Cebivqr fbzr "cebbs" guvf nyy jbexf cebcreyl.
